.040 |pmid=24631241}}</ref> | Gen. et sp. nov | Valid | Siveter ''et al.'' | Ordovician ([[Katian]]) | Lorraine Group | {{Flag|United States}} | A [[Myodocopa|myodocope]] [[ostracod]]. The type species is ''Luprisca incuba''. | |- | ''[[Martillepas]]<ref name=PGAcirripedes /> | Gen. et comb. nov | Valid | Gale | Late Jurassic | | {{Flag|United Kingdom}} | A [[Zeugmatolepadidae|zeugmatolepadid]] [[barnacle]]. A new genus for ''"[[Calantica]]" ovalis'' Withers (1928), ''"[[Zeugmatolepas]]" costata'' Withers (1928) and ''"[[Zeugmatolepas]]" hollisi'' Withers (1928). | |- | ''[[Masticacheles]]<ref name="fraaijeetalapp" /> | Gen et 2 sp nov | Valid | Fraaije ''et al.'' | [[Oxfordian (stage)|Oxfordian]] to [[Kimmeridgian]] | | {{Flag|Germany}}<br> {{Flag|Poland}} | A [[Parapylochelidae|parapylochelid]] [[hermit crab]]. The type species is ''Masticacheles longirostris'' from Oxfordian of Poland;<ref name="fraaijeetalapp" /> subsequently a second species ''Masticacheles minimus'' from late Kimmeridgian of Germany was named by Fraaije (2014).<ref name=NJGPAanomurans /> | |- | ''[[Mesoparapylocheles|Mesoparapylocheles jaegeri]]<ref name=NJGPAanomurans /> | Sp. nov | Valid | Fraaije | Late Jurassic (late [[Kimmeridgian]]) | | {{Flag|Germany}} | A [[hermit crab]], a species of ''Mesoparapylocheles''. | |- | ''[[Mesoparapylocheles|Mesoparapylocheles schweigerti]]<ref name=NJGPAanomurans /> | Sp. nov | Valid | Fraaije | Late Jurassic (late [[Kimmeridgian]]) | | {{Flag|Germany}} | A [[hermit crab]], a species of ''Mesoparapylocheles''. | |- | ''Monoceratina hussonae<ref name=JSP134ostracods /> | Sp. nov | Valid<ref name=JSP134ostracodsZB /> | Forel | Early Triassic | [[Kokarkuyu Formation]] | {{Flag|Turkey}} | An [[ostracod]], a species of ''[[Monoceratina]]''. | |- | ''[[Montemagrellus]]''<ref name=Corallomursia /> | Gen. et sp. nov | Valid | De Angeli & Ceccon | Early Eocene | | {{Flag|Italy}} | A crab belonging to the family [[Crossotonotidae]]. Genus includes new species ''M. 